<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Document</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    /* Style inputs with type="text", select elements and textareas */
    input[type=text],
    select,
    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      /* Full width */
      padding: 12px;
      /* Some padding */
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      /* Gray border */
      border-radius: 4px;
      /* Rounded borders */
      box-sizing: border-box;
      /* Make sure that padding and width stays in place */
      margin-top: 6px;
      /* Add a top margin */
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      /* Bottom margin */
      resize: vertical
        /* Allow the user to vertically resize the textarea (not horizontally) */
    }

    /* Style the submit button with a specific background color etc */
    input[type=submit] {
      background-color: #04AA6D;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    /* When moving the mouse over the submit button, add a darker green color */
    input[type=submit]:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }

    /* Add a background color and some padding around the form */
    .container {
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 8%;
      margin-left: 20%;
      margin-right: 20%;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div>
    <div class="container">
      <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="location.href ='/main'" data-toggle="modal"
        data-target="#myModalAdd">Main</button>
      <p></p>
      <p></p>
      <form action='/emailed' method="get">

        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Your name.." value={{email}}>

        <label for="subject">Subject</label>
        <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" placeholder="Subject" value="Company accounts">


        <label for="content">Content</label>


        <textarea id="content" name="content" value="vinu" placeholder="Write something.." style="height:400px">
Hi,
          
Hope you are well.
          
{{data2.coname}} - accounting period {{data2.period_start_on}} to {{data2.next_made_up_to}}          
          
I am writing to request the following information for the above mentioned accounting period:

1)  Financial Statements from all company bank accounts
2)  Sales, purchases and expense invoices
3)  List of debtors and creditors as at {{data2.next_made_up_to}}
4)  Any other information which would enable you to prepare accounts in a more accurate manner.
                
The company accounts submission deadline is on {{data2.next_due}} and there will be a penalty of up to Â£3,000 if they are not submitted on time. I would be grateful if you could provide me with the requested information as soon as possible.

Kind regards,
          
</textarea>
<script>
function copyText() {
  var textArea = document.getElementById("content");
  var text = textArea.value;
  var clipboard = navigator.clipboard;
  clipboard.writeText(text);
}

document.getElementById("copyButton").onclick = copyText;
</script>
        <button id="copyButton">Copy</button>



        <input type="submit" value="Sent email">



      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>

</html>
